%N A395336 a(n) = n! * [x^n] exp(x)/(2 - x - exp(x)).
%C A395336 a(n) is the number of homogeneous linear orderings in n colors (see Gonzalez).
%H A395336 David Gonzalez, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.14255">Enumerative Combinatorics of Homogeneous Linear Orderings</a>, arXiv:2604.14255 [math.CO], 2026. See Theorem 4.8 on pages 11-13.
%t A395336 terms=21; CoefficientList[Series[Exp[x]/(2-x-Exp[x]),{x,0,terms-1}],x]*Range[0,terms-1]!
